            <h1 style="margin-top:0">Cold Pi - Secure Bitcoin Storage</h1>

            <p>
                The Cold Pi allows you to store you bitcoins securely by keeping them on an air gapped device that you
                can carry with you.
            </p>

            <p>
                Using the Cold Pi is easy, simply insert the provided SDHC card to your Cold Pi and plug it to an HDMI
                source.
            </p>

            <p>We've pre-installed Bitcoin Armory on the Cold Pi along with bitaddress.org's source code. This will allow you to manage your coins, create
                paper-wallets and more..</p>

